headline: Software Development Stocks Q4 Results: Benchmarking Datadog (NASDAQ:DDOG)
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Datadog (NASDAQ:DDOG) and the rest of the software development stocks fared in Q4.
